content.rendered: Make cats by clicking. The cat bubbles growth accelerates when you start buying upgrades that increase the number of cat bubbles in production. Eventually, you’ll spawn billions of cat bubbles with each click, sending the cat world spiralling into a cuteness endless tunnel. You can use the reset button to start over and receive a permanent buff on your next game if you feel like a fresh start.
